As for the viscosity of the slurry, assuming that the suspension is hydrodynamically homogeneous, a theoretical formula proposed by Einstein to predict the viscosity of dilute suspensions of hard shell spheres can be applied:2μslurry=μcarrierfluid(1+kϕ)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
